transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Jimmy. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Jimmy, I got a trial of your SCORE Blue.

Speaker 1: It arrived probably two weeks ago.

Speaker 2: I have tried it five times with absolutely no results.

Speaker 1: So for me...

Speaker 2: Hey, is this Mike I'm speaking to?

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: Mike, let me ask you something. I'm looking at your account here.

Speaker 1: Did you place your order online?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: And were you trying to get the AGB? I believe you're probably trying to get the AGB, right?

Speaker 2: I assume so.

Speaker 1: Yeah, because I'm looking at your account.

Speaker 2: There's been a couple of times where a client orders online trying to try the new and improved Viagra AGB,

Speaker 1: and they don't push the right button, and then they get the generic Viagra.

Speaker 2: I see you got the 100 milligrams of generic Viagra.

Speaker 1: And the most popular Viagra is the AGB.

Speaker 2: And from what you described, I can look at right now, you didn't get the AGB.

Speaker 1: You got the regular generic Viagra.

Speaker 2: So I'll tell you what I'm going to do for you, Mike.

Speaker 1: I'm going to get you sent out that AGB, 10 of those, to replace that order that you got,

Speaker 2: because the AGB, you won't be calling and saying that something didn't work for you.

Speaker 1: I can guarantee you that.

Speaker 2: So I'm going to go ahead and take care of that for you.

Speaker 1: I'm going to ship you out 10 of those at no charge.

Speaker 2: And let me tell you the difference of the AGB and how that's going to look.

Speaker 1: It's going to be a white-shaped diamond peel, and it's going to have the number 100 on the back.

Speaker 2: That's how you can tell the AGB, and when you take it, you're going to see a drastic difference.

Speaker 1: So I'm going to get you those out today with no charge, and sorry for the mix-up.

Speaker 2: And let me tell you, you're going to want these again.

Speaker 1: When you want to order again, call us.

Speaker 2: Don't do it online, because if you go online, there's a good chance you're just going to get the generic Viagra.

Speaker 1: So normally the AGB is for existing clients only that has repeat orders.

Speaker 2: But, you know, I'm going to make sure you get those to try them.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Very good.

Speaker 1: I'll look forward to that and hopefully see better results.

Speaker 2: Exactly.

Speaker 1: You should see them within the next five to seven business days.

Speaker 2: They'll be out to you.

Speaker 1: Okay?

Speaker 2: Very good.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Not a problem.

Speaker 2: Take care.

Speaker 1: Bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
